Panzer::

She stopped in her tracks as she thought she heared the faint sound 
of an engine or two coming her way.  She shook her head and pressed 
on.  She skipped down a rock face and towards another meadow. the 
sounds seemed to get louder and louder.  She stopped and stood, 
facing the direction of the noice.  She sniffed the wind. Bots! But 
what bots?  She waited untill she could see them.
